These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, lavender, white
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bolivar, game
1. the bolivar-smoker is the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who likes white is between the game-smoker and the person who likes lavender##2
3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Color      | lavender | white | coral |
| Cigar   | bolivar     | dunhill    | game   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, aquamarine, turquise
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, satire, documentary
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching action movies and the person who likes emerald##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Color   | emerald    | turquise        | aquamarine |
| Movie-Genre     | satire | documentary | action         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, may
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, punk, hip-hop
1. the fan pop is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is between the fan punk and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Birthday   | december | november     | may |
| Music-Genre        | punk  | hip-hop | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking, chess
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, van, subway
1. the person who's hobby is reading is the person driving the car##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person driving the van and the person driving the car##2
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | chess     | reading |
| Transport           | van | subway | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, chinese, british
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, cola
1. the british is on the left of the polish##1
2. the british is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Nationality   | chinese | british     | polish |
| Beverage     | cola    | mirinda | 7up    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different pets are kept: rat, dog, goldfish
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, grapes, eggplant
1. the person eating kiwi is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the rat##2
2. the owner of the rat is the person eating grapes##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Pet   | rat  | dog   | goldfish        |
| Food         | grapes | kiwi | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, old-henry, siglo
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, bus
1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the siglo-smoker and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar          | old-henry  | fonseca  | siglo |
| Transport   | scooter | helicopter | bus     |

