.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, scooter, taxi
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, puzzles, video-games
1. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the taxi##2
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | taxi   | ship  | scooter  |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | puzzles | video-games |

