.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, december, august
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, cat
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | june | december   | august   |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | cat | chinchilla |

