2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | video-games | gardening   | photography   |
| Cigar         | baccarat  | old-henry | vegafina |

