.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, golf
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, singing, filmmaking
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is singing##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Sport      | golf | soccer   | handball |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | fishing | singing   |

 